gnu.awt
Interface PixelsOwner

All Known Implementing Classes:
VirtualFrame, VirtualJFrame, VNCPixels
public interface PixelsOwner

Access to a rectangular pixel raster as an array. Pixel arrays are composed of integers, with each integer corresponding to a pixel. The arrangement is left to right, top to bottom.
